21 supervision for each ten hours of core function performance shall be
22 documented. Supervisory methods shall include, as a minimum, individual
23 supervisory sessions, formal case staffings, and conjoint, cotherapy
24 sessions. Supervision shall be directed towards teaching the knowledge
25 and skills of professional alcohol and drug counseling.
